This is the complete run of X-Factor v3, featuring Jamie Madrox as the lead character and Peter David returning as head writer. The series focuses on the new X-Factor team and their many issues, along with crossing over with the other X-Men titles for several major storylines (including Decimation and Messiah CompleX). Well worth the read if you are a fan of previous incarnations of the team, or love Peter David's work. 

This series actually carries on from the Madrox: Multiple Choice miniseries, which you can find here, thanks to STFMaryville: &lt;a href=&quot;
http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/7960476&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; target=&quot;_NEW&quot;&gt;
http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/7960476&lt;/a&gt;

This torrent contains digital copies of all 50 issues, as well as the two specials that feature in this run - Layla Miller and The Quick And The Dead. Every copy is courtesy of Son of Ultron-Empire in high-res, except for Layla Miller which is by Cypher-Empire (also in HQ). Thanks to the scanner groups for their awesome efforts; these issues look great. Please seed and enjoy. 

